%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20West's%20drone%20tech%20risks%20becoming%20irrelevant%20if%20it's%20not%20tested%20daily%20on%20the%20Ukrainian%20battlefield%2C%20defense%20exec%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raybird%2C%20an%20ISTAR%20drone%20developed%20by%20Ukrainian%20company%20Skyeton%2C%20takes%20off%20against%20a%20blue%20sky%20from%20its%20launcher%2C%20with%20a%20person%20in%20army%20clothing%20behind.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6863dcbf85e81483682d1b1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20UK%20contractor%20teamed%20with%20a%20Ukrainian%20company%20to%20bring%20its%20Raybird%20surveillance%20drone%20to%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3ESkyeton%20Press%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Ukrainian%20company%20teamed%20with%20a%20UK%20contractor%20to%20bring%20its%20battle-tested%20drone%20to%20the%20UK%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20has%20become%20ground%20zero%20for%20developing%20cutting-edge%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUK-Ukraine%20tech-sharing%20aims%20to%20enhance%20military%20capabilities%20and%20retain%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dizzying%20pace%20of%20drone%20development%20is%20now%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20the%20fastest-moving%20companies%20are%20battle-testing%20their%20products%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20real-world%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20Western%20militaries%20understand%20that%20their%20drone%20tech%20will%20be%20functionally%20obsolete%20unless%20the%20technology%20they%20import%20or%20develop%20is%20field-tested%20in%20conflicts%20like%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20system%20is%20not%20in%20day-to-day%20use%20on%20the%20frontline%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20quickly%20out%20of%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Hedges%2C%20a%20former%20Royal%20Marine%20and%20cofounder%20of%20military%20intelligence%20company%20Prevail%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevail%20has%20partnered%20with%20Ukrainian%20drone%20company%20Skyeton%20to%20bring%20Raybird%2C%20a%20small%20surveillance%20and%20targeting%20drone%2C%20to%20production%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20being%20done%20with%20a%20shrewd%20eye%20on%20the%20British%20Army's%20plans%20to%20replace%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fcommentary%2Freplacing-watchkeeper-staying-behind-curve%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etroubled%20Watchkeeper%20drone%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20uncrewed%20surveillance%20and%20targeting%20capability%20more%20suited%20to%20the%20scenarios%20playing%20out%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Ffront-line-drone-technology-to-fuel-uk-ukraine-partnership%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20and%20drone%20tech-sharing%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20between%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20and%20the%20UK's%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20said%20that%20Ukrainian%20insight%20is%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bplugged%20into%20UK%20production%20lines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20chimes%20with%20a%20drive%20across%20the%20West%20to%20see%20the%20Ukrainian%20battlefield%20as%20a%20live%20laboratory%20%E2%80%94%20out%20of%20necessity%20for%20the%20country's%20defense%2C%20but%20increasingly%2C%20as%20a%20crucial%20way%20for%20smaller%20companies%20to%20develop%20systems%20and%20services%20that%20have%20a%20technological%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20armed%20forces%20minister%20Luke%20Pollard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-companies-without-ukraine-battlefield-presence-give-up-uk-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunderscored%20the%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20drone%20conference%20in%20Latvia%20in%20late%20May%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20drone%20company%20and%20you%20do%20not%20have%20your%20kit%20on%20the%20frontline%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20you%20might%20as%20well%20give%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaybird%2C%20Skyeton's%20drone%2C%20has%20a%20combined%20350%2C000%20hours%20of%20flight%20time%20on%20Ukraine's%20front%20line%2C%20in%20use%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20the%20Black%20Sea%20to%20Kharkiv%2C%26quot%3B%20Skyeton's%20founder%20Alex%20Stepura%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Stepura%2C%20Raybird%20can%20fly%20more%20than%2028%20continuous%20hours%20and%20uses%20an%20array%20of%20sensors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20optical%2C%20electromagnetic%2C%20and%20various%20radar%20capabilities%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collect%20data%20from%20%26quot%3Bfar%20behind%26quot%3B%20the%20front%20line%2C%20sometimes%20from%20more%20than%20125%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20its%20sensors%20can%20be%20swapped%20out%20in%20a%20minute%2C%20enabling%20forces%20to%20react%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20catapult%20setup%20for%20the%20Ukrainian%20Raybird%20small%20reconaissance%20drone%20Skybird.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6864e09685e81483682d30dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaybird%20can%20be%20set%20up%20within%2028%20minutes%2C%20its%20manufacturers%20say.%3Cp%3ESkyeton%20Press%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmod.gov.ua%2Fnews%2Fraybird-malenka-ptashka-z-mozhlivostyami-velikogo-litaka%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehailed%20the%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20being%20capable%20of%20tasks%20normally%20reserved%20for%20much%20larger%20models.%20Its%20size%20%E2%80%94%20just%2025kg%2C%20or%2055%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20gives%20an%20added%20advantage%3A%20it's%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20stealthy%2C%26quot%3B%20Hedges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESma