n%20if%20I'm%20still%20navigating%20the%20financial%20side%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ef18b2f-323a-44bc-8ebc-81e29713dbe7%5C%22%3EColonoscopy%20or%20stool%20test%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20a%20GI%20appointment%20after%20reading%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkatie-couric-shares-early-colon-cancer-signs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20stool%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20detect%20cancer%20via%20stool%20samples.%20It%20seemed%20minimally%20invasive%20while%20still%20taking%20some%20sort%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20appointment%2C%20I'd%20hoped%20my%20age%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-common-symptoms-colon-cancer-under-50s-chart-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20severe%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20abdominal%20pain%20would%20sway%20her%20to%20recommend%20the%20stool%20test%20over%20the%20colonoscopy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cologuard%20test%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686403f33d5881a51c1c7171%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStool%20tests%20like%20Cologuard%20are%20good%20at%20detecting%20cancer%2C%20but%20not%20preventing%20it.%3Cp%3ECologuard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20stool%20tests%20aren't%20considered%20the%20gold%20standard%20of%20colon%20cancer%20screenings%20because%20they%20can%20only%20detect%20cancer.%20It%20was%20possible%20that%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-had-potentially-precancerous-polyp-removed-in-colonoscopy-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprecancerous%20polyps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20which%20wouldn't%20show%20up%20in%20a%20stool%20test%20but%20could%20be%20safely%20removed%20and%20biopsied%20in%20a%20colonoscopy.%20Plus%2C%20colonoscopies%20can%20identify%20other%20colon-cancer-like%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-misdiagnosis-young-people-ibs-gluten-allergy-symptoms-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehemorrhoids%20or%20IBD%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20GI%20performed%20a%20quick%20rectal%20exam%20and%20didn't%20find%20anything.%20She%20said%20that%20given%20my%20age%2C%20the%20bleeding%20was%20likely%20caused%20by%20internal%20hemorrhoids%20or%20polyps%2C%20not%20cancer.%20She%20recommended%20I%20get%20a%20colonoscopy%20and%20some%20blood%20work%20to%20test%20my%20iron%20levels%2C%20which%20could%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolorectal-cancer-high-mortality-young-people-signs-symptoms-disease-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoint%20to%20colon%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20booked%20a%20colonoscopy%20for%20three%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261e14b27-7b74-4479-987c-e3d17f5ce718%5C%22%3EI%20was%20worried%20about%20the%20cost%20and%20intensity%20of%20the%20procedure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20blood%20work%20came%20back%20normal%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20I%20was%20overreacting.%20Did%20I%20really%20need%20a%20colonoscopy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20it%20was%20expensive.%20The%20procedure%20would%20cost%20%242%2C000%20total%20without%20insurance.%20My%20GI%20explained%20that%20because%20my%20test%20was%20diagnostic%20and%20being%20done%20to%20examine%20colon%20cancer%20symptoms%20(as%20opposed%20to%20a%20standard%20colon%20cancer%20screening)%2C%20it%20applied%20to%20my%20deductible.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20the%20cost%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20my%20insurance%20plan%2C%20how%20far%20into%20the%20deductible%20I%20am%2C%20and%20where%20the%20colonoscopy%20is%20being%20done.%20Because%20I%20did%20mine%20at%20a%20free-standing%20endoscopy%20center%20instead%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20it%20cut%20down%20on%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estimate%20I%20got%20from%20my%20insurance%20company%20was%20around%20%24813.%20That%20didn't%20include%20other%20potential%20fees%20like%20biopsies.%20This%20is%20still%20lower%20than%20the%20national%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodrx.com%2Fconditions%2Fcolon-cancer%2Fcolonoscopy-cost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20cost%20for%20a%20colonoscopy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%241%2C250%2C%20and%20some%20of%20my%20coworkers%20under%2045%20were%20quoted%20closer%20to%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221530%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cost%20estimate%20for%20a%20colonoscopy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686404a1f748d8c055f4b938%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20estimate%20I%20got%20prior%20to%20the%20procedure.%20I%20was%20also%20told%20that%20laboratory%20fees%2C%20like%20biopsies%2C%20could%20cost%20extra.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20the%20procedure%20itself%20felt%20intense%2C%20too.%20I'd%20need%20to%20fast%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaxatives-shortage-constipation-hybrid-work-fiber-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20about%20%2440%20of%20laxatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Gatorade%20the%20night%20before%2C%20undergo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fanesthesia-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanesthesia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20have%20my%20husband%20pick%20me%20up.%20There%20were%20also%20very%20rare%20risks%2C%20like%20tears%20to%20my%20colon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20times%20a%20week%2C%20I'd%20approach%20my%20husband%20forlornly%2C%20asking%20him%20if%20he%20thought%20I%20was%20overreacting%20and%20should%20skip%20the%20procedure.%20Sadly%2C%20I%20learned%20the%20hard%20truth%3A%20no%20one%20could%20make%20this%20decision%20but%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPostponing%20would%20be%20complicated%2C%20given%20our%20future%20plans%20to%20have%20kids%3A%20I%20can't%20get%20a%20colonoscopy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbloody-stool-pregnancy-hemorrhoids-colorectal-cancer-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce%20I'm%20pregnant%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20risks%20to%20the%20fetus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20that%20I%20was%20fortunate%3A%20I%20had%20time%20to%20pre-plan%20and%20budget%20my%20colonoscopy%2C%20I%20could%20easily%20take%20a%20sick%20day%20from%20work%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20could%20take%20a%20few%20hours%20off%20from%20his%20job%20to%20pick%20me%20up.%20If%20I%20was%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%20now%20was%20absolutely%20the%20best%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228916fde1-0162-47ce-9641-705a1ed9cb73%5C%22%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20did%20it%2C%20but%20insurance%20is%20a%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20start%20with%20the%20bad%20news%3A%20months%20after%20the%20procedure%2C%20I'm%20still%20dealing%20with%20insurance%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20sure%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-use-fsa-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFSA%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20pre-tax%20money%20I%20elected%20to%20set%20aside%20for%20medical%20costs%2C%20would%20cover%20at%20least%20most%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20any%20extra%20fees.%20But%20because%20my%20receipt%20was%20missing%20information%2C%20the%20reimbursement%20for%20%24813%20was%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20complete%20receipt%2C%20I%20was%20told%20I'd%20need%20to%20wait%2030-60%20days%20for%20my%20insurance%20to%20process%20my%20itemized%20statement.%20While%20I%20was%20waiting%2C%20I%20was%20mailed%20two%20more%20bills%3B%20%24124.08%20for%20a%20physician's%20processing%20fee%20and%20%24125.40%20for%20the%20anesthesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20colonoscopy%20bills%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686404f7f748d8c055f4b953%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20assumed%20these%20costs%20were%20already%20covered%20in%20the%20colonoscopy%20fee%2C%20which%20was%20over%20%24800.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20holding%20on%20to%20them%20until%20I%20get%20reimbursed%20for%20the%20%24813.%20Otherwise%2C%20I'd%20be%20paying%20over%20%241%2C000%20out%20of%20pocket%2C%20with%20no%20clarity%20on%20when%20I'll%20actually%20get%20the%20money%20back%2C%20if%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db87b3ed-d00c-454c-85d7-b1522b5c270f%5C%22%3EI%20finally%20had%20answers%20for%20my%20symptoms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%3A%20the%20colonoscopy%20itself%20went%20smoothly.%20Sure%2C%20induced%20bowel%20cleansing%20wasn't%20my%20idea%20of%20a%20riveting%20Wednesday%20night.%20But%20from%20speaking%20to%20multiple%20people%20who've%20had%20colonoscopies%2C%20it%20sounds%20like%20it%20wasn't%20as%20unpleasant%20as%20chugging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC3566661%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolytely%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20common%20colonoscopy%20prep%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20procedure%20took%20about%2020%20minutes%2C%20all%20of%20which%20I%20was%20out%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20my%20GI%20popped%20in%20to%20explain%20my%20results.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20relief%20to%20have%20answers.%20Like%20she%20suspected%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-symptoms-young-people-misdiagnosed-hemorrhoids-women-worldclass-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternal%20hemorrhoids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20swollen%20veins%20in%20the%20anus%20and%20lower%20rectum%2C%20were%20causing%20the%20bleeding.%20Hemorrhoids%20are%20fairly%20common%20in%20young%20people%2C%20and%20activities%20like%20lifting%20heavy%20weights%20could%20cause%20them.%20Looking%20back%2C%20the%20bleeding%20began%20around%20when%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealized-protein-intake-was-low-when-began-weightlifting-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20GI%20confirmed%20that%20it%20could%20exacerbate%20the%20hemorrhoids.%20I%20can%20manage%20them%20by%20drinking%20more%20water%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-fiber-high-protein-food-plant-based-sources-nutritionist-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeating%20more%20fiber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20using%20hydrocortisone%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20found%20and%20removed%20two%20polyps%2C%20one%20of%20which%20could%20be%20precancerous%20because%20of%20its%20size.%20A%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20a%20biopsy%20confirmed%20that%20the%20polyp%20was%20benign%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20get%20another%20colonoscopy%20until%20I'm%2045%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fwhen-to-get-first-colonoscopy-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecommended%20starting%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20colon%20cancer%20screenings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rate%20of%20colorectal%20cancer%20rises%20among%20young%20people%2C%20there%20is%20a%20push%20for%20people%20to%20get%20their%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-about-colon-cancer-symptoms-diagnosis-chadwick-boseman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolon%20cancer%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20checked%20out.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBut%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20anyone%20under%20the%20recommended%20screening%20age%20would%20skip%20a%20colonoscopy.%20Beyond%20the%20financial%20obstacle%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20quick%20procedure%20and%20requires%20a%20support%20system.%20It's%20easy%20to%20feel%20like%20the%20potential%20downside%20%E2%80%94%20spending%20time%20an