0command%20and%20control%20vessel%20USS%20Mount%20Whitney%20and%20the%20guided-missile%20destroyer%20USS%20Paul%20Ignatius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20force%20deployed%20a%20naval%20drone%20called%20the%20Global%20Autonomous%20Reconnaissance%20Craft%20and%20other%20systems%20for%20the%20exercise.%20This%20system%2C%20made%20by%20the%20US%20company%20BlackSea%20Technologies%2C%20resembles%20a%20small%20speedboat%20and%20can%20sprint%20up%20to%2040%20knots%2C%20or%2046%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMattis%20said%20that%20the%20goal%20was%20to%20put%20the%20ships%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20they%20had%20to%20react%20on%20an%20uncomfortably%20short%20timeline.%20In%20some%20of%20the%20training%20scenarios%2C%20operators%20would%20have%20a%20drone%20tail%20one%20of%20the%20larger%20vessels%20and%20then%20suddenly%20sprint%20out%20from%20behind%20it%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20react.%20In%20other%20situations%2C%20multiple%20drone%20boats%20attacked%20from%20different%20angles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20with%20naval%20drones%20is%20that%20they%20are%20small%2C%20making%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthis-struck-merchant-ship-drone-disguised-fishing-boat-red-sea-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20difficult%20to%20detect%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20differentiate%20from%20various%20commercial%20boats.%20When%20operating%20in%20a%20normal%20routine%2C%20like%20in%20port%2C%20the%20watch%20team%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20threat%20before%20tragedy%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMattis%20said%20the%20exercise%20took%20place%20at%20the%20basic%20level%2C%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20creating%20what%20he%20described%20as%20a%20dilemma.%20He%20said%20this%20specific%20exercise%20was%20designed%20so%20sailors%20could%20understand%20the%20operating%20characteristics%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-boats-heat-seeking-missiles-scare-russian-aircraft-comm