sibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20homemade%20powders%20like%20peanut%20and%20sprouted%20ragi%20powder%2C%20along%20with%20Himalayan%20pink%20salt%2C%20black%20salt%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20flakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20essentials%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20ventured%20into%20ready-to-eat%20items.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20recently%20started%20offering%20homemade%20sweets%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20cupcakes%20made%20from%20millets%2C%20jaggery%2C%20and%20palm%20jaggery%20%E2%80%94%20healthy%20alternatives%20to%20rice%20flour%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20and%20white%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20customers%20are%20keen%20on%20organic%20products%2C%20but%20they%20often%20struggle%20to%20trust%20their%20authenticity.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20farms%2C%20and%20if%20they%20wish%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20order%20from%20the%20farmers%2C%20with%20us%20handling%20the%20delivery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreshte%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20authenticity%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20traditional%20processing%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20vacuum%20packing%20and%20oxygen%20absorbers%20to%20prevent%20pests%20naturally%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20process%20that%20helps%20us%20maintain%20the%20freshness%20and%20quality%20of%20our%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20five%20years%20of%20operation%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20reached%20impressive%20milestones%2C%20generating%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20and%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2090%20lakh.%20However%2C%20for%20Manikanta%20and%20Pavani%2C%20the%20true%20measure%20of%20success%20goes%20beyond%20financial%20achievements.%20They%20take%20immense%20pride%20in%20the%20positive%20impact%20they%20have%20on%20their%20customers%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being.%20%E2%80%9COur%20aim%20is%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20what%20they%20eat%20and%20embrace%20healthier%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20organic%20food%20to%20become%20a%20way%20of%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20farmers%20and%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20extends%20not%20only%20to%20their%20customers%20but%20also%20to%20their%20community.%20Sreshte%20currently%20collaborates%20with%2055%20farmers%2C%20empowering%20them%20with%20fair%20prices%20and%20stable%20markets%20for%20their%20produce.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20employ%2010%20dedicated%20staff%20members%20who%20assist%20with%20packaging%20and%20delivery%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20local%20economy%20and%20providing%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESesha%20Rao%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Guntur%20district%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20grateful%20to%20work%20with%20Sreshte%2C%20as%20they%20ensure%20I%20receive%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20my%20natural%20farming%20practices%20with%20chillies.%20Their%20support%20has%20not%20only%20encouraged%20me%20to%20continue%20with%20organic%20farming%2C%20but%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20grow%20professionally%20by%20enabling%20me%20to%20sell%20my%20chillies%20and%20chilli%20powder%20directly%20to%20customers.%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20continuing%20this%20path%20and%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20organic%20farming%20community%20with%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20measure%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20success%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20stories%20of%20its%20customers.%20Nandana%2C%20a%20regular%20shopper%20from%20Rajendranagar%2C%20Guntur%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20prefer%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20organic%20foods%20because%20they%20are%20fr