er.com%2Fcoast-guard-infrastructure-in-shambles-will-cost-billions-to-fix-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Coast%20Guard%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20college%20sophomore%20in%201996.%20After%20graduating%2C%20I%20was%20stationed%20on%20a%20ship%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20chasing%20drug%20runners%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20transitioned%20into%20crisis%20management%20and%20moved%20four%20times%20over%20the%20next%2012%20years.%20I%20responded%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-harvey-katrina-comparison-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHurricane%20Katrina%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202005%20and%20worked%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20as%20a%20congressional%20fellow%20for%20the%20late%20Congressman%20Elijah%20Cummings%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20my%20career%20and%20learned%20from%20some%20exceptional%20leaders.%20I%20also%20had%20the%20misfortune%20of%20surviving%20a%20few%20toxic%20ones.%20I%20was%20one%20of%2050%20Black%20women%20officers%20out%20of%20nearly%2050%2C000%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20my%20competence%20was%20questioned%20regularly.%20I%20worked%2080%20hours%20weekly%20to%20prove%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238054ef7-8b06-4f1d-9e1a-218f73c2eb79%5C%22%3EI%20worked%20from%20sunup%20to%20sundown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20for%20professional%20certifications%20at%20night%20and%20obtained%20several%20advanced%20degrees.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-work-life-balance-advice-boss-lessons-job-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWork-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20impossible%2C%20and%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20awards%20I%20received%2C%20I%20was%20never%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20executive%20level%20and%20relocated%20to%20Port%20Arthur%2C%20Texas.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20a%20former%20toxic%20boss%20became%20my%20supervisor%20again%2C%20and%20everything%20started%20to%20un