le%20to%20receive%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20month%20because%20my%20mental%20and%20physical%20condition%20rendered%20me%20incapable%20of%20working%20to%20earn%20an%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20not%20to%20submit%20the%20paperwork%20because%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20fully%20recover%20if%20I%20worked%20just%20as%20hard%20on%20myself%20as%20I%20had%20in%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pursued%20wholeness%2C%20and%20it%20took%20two%20years%20to%20heal%20physically%2C%20four%20years%20to%20recover%20mentally%2C%20and%20seven%20years%20to%20recover%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffaaea16-dab4-446d-a277-402362f034be%5C%22%3EI%20did%20five%20things%20to%20recover%20mentally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20discovered%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fself-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eself-care%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20made%20it%20a%20habit.%20I%20started%20meditating%2C%20working%20out%2C%20and%20walking%20at%20least%20three%20times%20a%20week.%20I%20also%20started%20sleeping%20eight%20hours%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stopped%20watching%20the%20news.%20Since%20the%20news%20was%20primarily%20negative%2C%20it%20didn't%20make%20me%20feel%20good%20about%20myself%20or%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20off%20my%20superhero%20cape%20and%20changed%20my%20phone%20number.%20I%20had%20to%20stop%20trying%20to%20save%20everyone%20else%20and%20myself%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20deleted%20social%20media%20for%2018%20months.%20I%20couldn't%20process%20all%20the%20information%20I%20consumed.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20lying%20about%20my%20life%20while%20watching%20everyone%20else%20lie%20about%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20forgave%20my%20family.%20Being%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20in%20my%20family%20to%20graduate%20from%20college%2C%20I%20was%20terrified%20of%20failure.%20When%20my%20worst%20nightmare%20came%20true%2C%20and%20I%20failed%20and%20lost%20everything%2C%20I%20realized%20they%20didn't%20need%20to%20change%3B%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ce0abbc-de12-49a3-ade3-1c504fe8799a%5C%22%3EI%20also%20did%20five%20things%20to%20recover%20financially%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20was%20accepted%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-went-to-harvard-business-school-here-is-what-you-should-know%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20solid%20past%20and%20a%20grand%20vision%20of%20the%20future%2C%20but%20a%20messy%20present%20moment%20of%20nothingness.%20The%20Program%20for%20Leadership%20Development%20helped%20me%20translate%20military%20language%20into%20corporate%20terminology%2C%20enabling%20me%20to%20market%20my%20leadership%20development%20services%20effectively.%20I%20saw%20my%20habits%20of%20exhaustive%20working%20and%20self-neglect%20reflected%20in%20my%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20published%20five%20books%20in%20eight%20months%20and%20started%20coaching%20my%20HBS%20colleagues%20on%20their%20careers%20and%20burnout.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202017%2C%20I%20graduated%20from%20HBS%20and%20finally%20moved%20out%20of%20my%20brother's%20house.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-self-doubt-tips-finding-right-fit-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvested%20in%20a%20business%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%2010%20months%20later%2C%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20my%20rent%20and%20the%20coach%2C%20so%20I%20gave%20up%20my%20place%20and%20spent%20a%20year%20traveling%2C%20staying%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20while%20building%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20I%20started%20teaching%20leaders%20how%20to%20recover%20from%20burnout%20by%20appealing%20to%20their%20desire%20for%20career%20advancement.%20I%20had%20my%20first%206-figure%20year%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%20a%20te