m.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%2020%20years%20in%20tech%2C%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20as%20clearly%20defined%20a%20market%20for%20extraordinary%20talent%20in%20a%20single%20category%20as%20for%20people%20who%20are%20capable%20of%20doing%20work%20on%20the%20frontier%20in%20AI%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Roy%20Bahat%2C%20the%20longtime%20head%20of%20VC%20firm%20Bloomberg%20Beta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa8039f0-994f-499e-a6bb-a6ae7b118236%5C%22%3EA%20shortage%20of%20talent%20and%20an%20excess%20of%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20the%20frenzy%20is%20the%20confluence%20of%20two%20factors%2C%20according%20to%20Bahat%20and%20others.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20researchers%20and%20engineers%20capable%20of%20building%20foundational%20models%20%E2%80%94%20something%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20of%202%2C000%20people.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20companies%20led%20by%20Meta%2C%20which%20is%20approaching%20a%20market%20capitalization%20of%20%242%20trillion%2C%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20spend%20almost%20anything%20to%20avoid%20falling%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20companies%20are%20just%20all%20so%20much%20bigger%20than%20they%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Bahat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bidding%20war%20is%20trickling%20down%20to%20classrooms%2C%20where%20companies%20are%20going%20after%20top%20machine-learning%20Ph.D.%20interns%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20pressuring%20them%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Bill%20Aulet%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Martin%20Trust%20Center%20for%20Entrepreneurship%20at%20MIT.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20dizzying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExplicit%20in%20the%20pitch%20for%20students%20is%20that%20advances%20in%20AI%20are%20happening%20so%20fast%20that%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20moment%20could%20be%20over%20by%20graduation%2C%20according%20to%20Bahat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20figuring%20out%20they%20spend%20these%20few%20precious%20years%20when%20this%20technology%20is%20at%20an%20inflection%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bahat.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20high-stakes%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20calculus%20has%20also%20changed%20for%20would-be%20founders%20thinking%20about%20starting%20foundational%20model%20startups%20who%20are%20daunted%20by%20how%20much%20they%20have%20to%20raise%2C%20according%20to%20Navin%20Chaddha%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20Mayfield%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20PhDs%20in%20the%20past%2C%20you%20could%20start%20a%20company%20for%20%245%20million%2C%20but%20now%20you%20may%20need%20to%20raise%20%2430%20to%20%2450%20million%20to%20pay%20starting%20salaries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20some%20would-be%3F%20founders%20stay%20at%20big%20tech%20companies%20because%20the%20salaries%20have%20gotten%20so%20high.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20because%20they%20have%20guaranteed%20money%20in%20the%20pocket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMira%20Murati%2C%20the%20former%20CTO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20has%20paid%20some%20talent%20around%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%20in%20salary%20for%20her%20new%20startup%2C%20Thinking%20Machines%20Lab%2C%20before%20even%20announcing%20a%20first%20funding%20round%20or%20a%20product%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmuratis-new-ai-startup-salary-technical-talent-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20reported%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20figure%20does%20not%20include%20equity%20or%20signing%20bonuses%2C%20which%20is%20where%20startup%20employees%20hope%20to%20make%20most%20of%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEye-popping%20new%20salaries%20side%2C%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20hope%20that%20startups%20can%20maintain%20their%20ethos%20that%20money%20isn't%20the%20only%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Wall%20Street%2C%20tech%20has%20long%20espoused%20a%20view%20of%20doing%20something%20good%20for%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20very%20elite%20levels%20for%20AI%20research%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20extremely%20values-driven%2C%20so%20not%20being%20mission-driven%20is%20a%20dead%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said.%20%26quot%3BUsually%20when%20you're%20not%20mission-driven%2C%20attrition%20is%20bad%20and%20productivity%20is%20poor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20tip%20to%20share%20about%20the%20AI%20recruiting%20wars%3F%20Contact%20reporter%20Ben%20Bergman%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20BenBergman.11%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751446801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68635ff485e81483682d17ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20ton%20of%20ripple%20effects%20I'm%20hearing%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deedy%20Das%2C%20of%20Menlo%20Ventures.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20jealousy%2C%20envy%2C%20and%20helplessness.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20tried%20Luckin%20Coffee's%20first%20US%20location%20in%20NYC.%20Starbucks%20should%20watch%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alice%20Tecotzky%20at%20Luckin%20Coffee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ins