20chai%20or%20a%20cappuccino%20if%20I'm%20feeling%20crazy.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20I'm%20not%20the%20ideal%20customer%20for%20fruit-infused%20cold%20brew%20or%20%26quot%3Biced%20coconut%20velvet%20latte%2C%26quot%3B%20whatever%20that%20entails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20sip%20of%20the%20pineapple%20cold%20brew%20just%20tasted%20like%20chunky%20pineapple%20juice%20%E2%80%94%20not%20bad%2C%20but%20not%20coffee.%20After%20some%20aggressive%20cup%20shaking%2C%20I%20took%20another%20sip.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20also%20tasted%20like%20chunky%20pineapple%20juice%2C%20just%20more%20watered%20down.%20Weirdly%2C%20I%20wasn't%20mad%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luckin%20Coffee's%20pineapple%20cold%20brew%20and%20solar%20breeze%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68641df6f748d8c055f4bd9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20pineapple%20cold%20brew%20and%20solar%20breeze.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solar%20breeze%20was%20pleasantly%20sour%20and%20also%20unexpectedly%20filled%20with%20orange%20chunks.%20I%20probably%20would've%20preferred%20it%20in%20the%20afternoon%20rather%20than%20at%2010%20am%2C%20but%20I%20can%20see%20why%20juice%20aficionados%20would%20be%20pleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBruce%20Leon%2C%2053%2C%20told%20me%20he%20actually%20liked%20the%20chunkiness%20of%20the%20pineapple%20cold%20brew%2C%20because%20it%20suggested%20the%20drink%20wasn't%20made%20from%20syrup.%20He%20said%20he'd%20never%20heard%20of%20Luckin%20before%2C%20but%20plans%20to%20come%20back%20with%20a%20friend.%20Chelsea%2C%2033%2C%20also%20didn't%20know%20about%20the%20brand%20but%20walked%20in%20because%20it's%20across%20from%20her%20subway%20stop.%20Her%20plain%20cold%20brew%20was%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Breally%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourtney%20Kraft%2C%2030%2C%20however%2C%20k