arget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20farmers%20can%20easily%20earn%20more%20profit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeranium%20is%20valued%20for%20its%20leaves%2C%20which%20are%20processed%20to%20extract%20essential%20oil.%20This%20oil%20is%20in%20high%20demand%20both%20in%20India%20and%20internationally.%20Once%20planted%2C%20geranium%20can%20be%20harvested%20four%20times%20a%20year%20for%20about%20four%20years%2C%20yielding%2015%E2%80%9316%20tons%20of%20leaves%20every%20three%20months.%20Geranium%20plants%20require%20less%20irrigation%20making%20them%20a%20practical%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20crops%20like%20paddy%20and%20pulses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20870px)%20100vw%2C%20870px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geranium%20farming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-500x347.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-768x533.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patade-family-1_10_11zon-1751287674-150x104.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELokesh%E2%80%99s%20fields%20yield%20up%20to%2050%E2%80%9360%20litres%20of%20oil%20per%20acre%20each%20year%2C%20and%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20natural%20resistance%20to%20pests%20means%20lower%20costs.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Bilaspur%2C%20Patade%20cultivates%20geranium%E2%80%94the%20Egyptian%20variety%20(Pelargonium%20graveolens)%20also%20called%20the%20Kelkar%20variety%E2%80%94on%20three%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20at%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20acre.%20Harvested%20every%20third%20or%20fourth%20month%2C%20a%20geranium%20plant%20continued%20to%20produce%20leaves%20for%20three%20to%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETraining%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20various%20medicinal%20and%20aromatic%20plants%20like%20lemongrass%20and%20palmarosa%20were%20already%20being%20cultivated%20in%20his%20region%2C%20geranium%20was%20largely%20unknown%20to%20local%20farmers.%20Geranium%20is%20widely%20grown%20both%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20and%2C%20like%20other%20aromatic%20plants%2C%20its%20essential%20oil%20can%20be%20refined%20and%20has%20a%20strong%20market%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Patade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeadow%20Agrotech%2C%20is%20an%20incubated%20startup%20of%20IGKV%20RABI%2C%20(Indira%20Gandhi%20Krishi%20Vishwavidyalaya%20%E2%80%93%20Research%20and%20Business%20Incubation)%2C%20located%20in%20Raipur%2C%20Chhattisgarh.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391351%2Fsarbeswar-basumatary-padma-shri-assam-agriculture-journey%2F%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20innovation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20business%20incubation%20hub%2C%20it%20supports%20startups%20and%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20agri-business%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20300px)%20100vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGeranium-saplings_3_11zon-1751287642.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geranium%20farming%20in%20Chhattisgarh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGeranium-saplings_3_11zon-1751287642.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGeranium-saplings_3_11zon-1751287642-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGeranium-saplings_3_11zon-1751287642-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458380%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Value%20Crop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Geranium%20offers%20a%20significant%20income%20opportunity%20for%20farmers%20due%20to%20its%20high%20market%20value.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20leading%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236549%2Fbihar-farmer-earns-lakhs-superfood-makhana-entrepreneur-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-cultivation-farming-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%3Etraining%20sessions%20for%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eacross%20Maharashtra%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20expand%20Geranium%20cultivation%2C%20to%20bring%20100%20acres%20under%20cultivation.%20Patade%20has%20gone%20beyond%20traditional%20farming%20by%20pioneering%20the%20production%20of%20hydrosol%20air%20fresheners%E2%80%94an%20innovation%20that%20marks%20a%20first%20for%20India.%20To%20support%20this%20venture%2C%20he%20established%20a%20distillation%20unit%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20500%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20hydrosol%20process%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanaka%2C%20recipient%20of%20the%20Academy%20of%20Plant%20Sciences%E2%80%99%20Young%20Scientist%20Award%20in%202009%20and%20author%20of%20several%20research%20papers%2C%20explains%20the%20hydrosol%20process.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20process%20helps%20preserve%20geranium%E2%80%99s%20therapeutic%20properties%20by%20capturing%20both%20water-soluble%20and%20some%20volatile%20components%20from%20the%20plant%20material%20during%20steam%20or%20water%20distillation.%20When%20geranium%20leaves%20and%20flowers%20are%20disti