re%20are%20five%20parameters%20before%20adopting%20the%20ERT%20to%20rejuvenate%20degraded%20land.%20According%20to%20the%20scientist%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESelection%20of%20the%20degraded%20area%20with%20the%20source%20of%20contaminants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EScreening%20and%20selection%20of%20tolerant%20plant%20species.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplication%20of%20desired%20microbial%20inoculants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmendment%20with%20organic%20substances%2C%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplication%20of%20desired%20fungal%20inoculants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20these%20parameters%20are%20accessed%2C%20we%20pick%20the%20bamboo%20sapling%20to%20be%20cultivated%20on%20the%20contaminated%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20selecting%20the%20bamboo%20sapling%20is%20a%20crucial%20process%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20says%20that%20picking%20a%20species%20of%20bamboo%20that%20consumes%20less%20water%20is%20important%2C%20as%20most%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20face%20water%20scarcity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20usually%20select%20a%20plant%20that%20is%20cost-friendly%20and%20has%20a%20high%20leaf%20persistence%20value.%20A%20leaf%20with%20a%20high%20leaf%20persistence%20value%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20wither%20away%20easily.%20The%20sapling%20should%20also%20be%20fast-growing%20and%20mitigate%20dust%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20scientist%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20green%20revolution%20beyond%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20breathing%20life%20back%20into%20the%20dusty%20lands%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Vidarbha%20region%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Lal%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20his%20team%20are%20not%20stopping.%20The%20success%20here%20has%20become%20a%20starting%20point%E2%80%94a%20blueprint%20for%20healing%20broken%20lands%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20next%20mission%20takes%20them%20to%20