ous%20about%20his%20background%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20him%20more%20about%20where%20he%20was%20from.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20said%20Khagaria%20%E2%80%94%20my%20own%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20That%20patient%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Bihar%20to%20Delhi%20%5B1%2C200%20kilometres%5D%20just%20for%20the%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20revelation%20shook%20him.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20presence%20of%20world-class%20medical%20care%20in%20places%20like%20Delhi%2C%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20services%20in%20my%20region.%20This%20experience%20lit%20a%20spark%20in%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20determination%20to%20work%20in%20my%20hometown%20and%20improve%20healthcare%20access%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20was%20working%20in%20the%20non-invasive%20cardiac%20department%20and%20had%20a%20clear%20path%20ahead%3A%20a%20stable%2C%20high-paying%20career%20in%20the%20city.%20But%20that%20single%20conversation%20awakened%20something%20deeper%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pull%20towards%20home%2C%20where%20healthcare%20was%20not%20a%20business%2C%20but%20a%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cities%2C%20healthcare%20is%20business%3B%20back%20home%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20survival%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20That%20became%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20mission%3A%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291947%2Fdelhi-doctor-neurologist-quits-united-states-job-give-affordable-healthcare-to-rural-bihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccessible%20healthcare%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20the%20people%20of%20his%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1751290124.jpg