r%20Rahman%20was%20just%20a%20child%20when%20he%20learnt%20one%20of%20life%E2%80%99s%20harshest%20lessons.%20Once%2C%20he%20accompanied%20his%20ailing%20mother%20and%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20two%20separate%20consultations%2C%20which%20led%20to%20humiliation%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20compounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20about%20five%20or%20six%20years%20old%20when%20my%20mother%20took%20me%20and%20my%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%2C%20so%20she%20asked%20the%20compounder%20if%20both%20of%20us%20could%20be%20treated%20under%20the%20same%20prescription%20to%20save%20money.%20He%20reacted%20harshly%2C%20scolding%20us%20for%20being%20poor.%20I%20was%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20everything%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20the%20shame%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%2C%20whom%20I%20revered%20and%20still%20consider%20my%20role%20model%2C%20was%20compassionate%20and%20did%20not%20treat%20us%20poorly.%20This%20experience%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indignity%20of%20being%20scolded%20for%20poverty%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20life%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20shaped%20his%20resolve%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398655%2Fdr-taru-jindal-doctor-improving-bihar-healthcare-district-hospital-maternal-care%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20healthcare%20for%20the%20underprivileged%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20vowed%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20become%20a%20doctor%20who%20never%20turns%20anyone%20away%20for%20lack%20of%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me