he%20commercial%20gain%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%2C%20above%20all%2C%20a%20sacred%20duty.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Rahman%2C%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20with%20the%20setting%20sun.%20Nights%20often%20find%20him%20attending%20to%20emergencies%2C%20sleeping%20only%20after%20ensuring%20patients%E2%80%99%20stability.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20operate%20between%2011%20am%20and%2011%20pm.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20need%20to%20extend%20working%20hours%2C%20too.%20Just%20last%20night%2Ctwo%20heart%20attack%20patients%20came%20in.%20I%20came%20back%20home%20after%20midnight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20he%20finds%20balance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20sleep%20soundly%20during%20non-working%20hours.%20This%20allows%20me%20to%20function%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20says%2C%20has%20been%20his%20lifestyle%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years.%20Over%20these%20years%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20impact%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20thousands%20of%20patients%20he%20has%20treated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20blessing%20during%20the%20darkest%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20patients%2C%20Hamza%20Khaild%2C%20recalls%20how%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20kindness%20saved%20his%20family%20from%20financial%20ruin.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20my%20father%20had%20a%20paralytic%20stroke%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20We%20admitted%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Begusarai%2C%20but%20in%20one%20week%2C%20the%20bill%20touched%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20We%20were%20devastated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20we%20consulted%20Dr%20Rahman%2C%20and%20he%20advised%20us%20to%20shift%20my%20father%20to%20the%20CCU%20at%20his%20hospital.%20We%20took%20him%20there%2C%20and%20we%20received%20immense%20support%20%E2%80%94%20they%20charged%20nothing%20for%20the%20CCU.%20Their%20kindness%20was%20a%20blessing%20during%20a%20challenging%20time%2C%20and%20they%20have%20aided%20many%20others%20similarly.%20I%20can%20never%20repay%20them%20for%20their%20generosity!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Rahman%20runs%20a%2050-bed%20hospital%20in%20Khagaria.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-4-1751290147-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rahman%20runs%20a%2050-bed%20hospital%20in%20Khagaria.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%2C%20under%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20workmanship%2C%20treats%20about%2070%20patients%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20whom%20cannot%20afford%20even%20the%20modest%20Rs%2050%20consultation%20fee.%20For%20him%2C%20medicine%20transcends%20the%20commercial%20gain%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%2C%20above%20all%2C%20a%20sacred%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20ever%20regrets%20leaving%20a%20high-paying%20job%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20replies%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20lead%20a%20simple%20life%2C%20free%20from%20material%20desires%2C%20and%20that%20brings%20me%20peace.%20More%20importantly%2C%20I%20have%20built%20a%20deep%20connection%20with%