ant-sustainable-architecture-and-recycled-wood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20used%20is%20recycled%20from%20old%20buildings%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20the%20labour%20inputs%20increase.%20At%20every%20point%20in%20the%20system%2C%20we%20have%20methods%20by%20which%20the%20involvement%20of%20people%20brings%20value%20to%20the%20building.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20learning%20in%20this%20womb%20of%20ecology%2C%20children%20grasp%20better.%20%3Cstrong%3EBut%20if%20this%20is%20to%20continue%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgive.do%2Ffundraisers%2Fmud-school-building-restoration-fundraiser%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20donation%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20what%20can%20you%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECulture%20and%20background%20have%20never%20been%20a%20talent%20differentiator%20at%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushpa%20Yadav%20(19)%20figured%20this%20out%20early%20on.%20On%20her%20first%20day%2C%20she%20was%20intimidated.%20Relegated%20to%20a%20life%20on%20the%20streets%20after%20her%20parents%20had%20passed%20away%2C%20Pushpa%20did%20not%20know%20the%20alphabet%20or%20how%20to%20count.%20But%20at%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%2C%20she%20learnt%20an%20important%20life%20lesson%20%E2%80%94%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20first%20time.%20Now%2C%20Pushpa%20coaches%20young%20girls%20in%20Frisbee.%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20teaching%20girls%20sports.%20It%E2%80%99s%20unfair%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20same%20opportunities%20as%20boys%3B%20girls%20always%20have%20to%20think%20twice%20before%20being%20allowed%20to%20do%20something.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pushpa%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20worry%20is%20child%20marriage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20stop%20this%20from%20happening.%20At%20least%20through%20education%20and%20sports%2C%20I%20feel%20we%20can%20help%20girls%20escape%20early%20marriages%20and%20other%20unhappy%20futures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pushpa%20adds.%20And%20she%20believes%20that%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%20will%20edify%20this%20hope%20for%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Sourabh%20Gujar%20(32)%20shares%20this%20belief.%20He%20is%20among%20the%20team%20of%20people%20restoring%20the%20school%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Learning%20in%20a%20school%20that's%20built%20out%20of%20mud%20helps%20children%20feel%20comfortable%20as%20it%20mimics%20their%20home%20settings%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-6-1751289234-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458432%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELearning%20in%20a%20school%20that%E2%80%99s%20built%20out%20of%20mud%20helps%20children%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20as%20it%20mimics%20their%20home%20settings%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20architects%20are%20also%20restoring%20the%20plinth%20around%20the%20building%20to%20keep%20water%20at%20bay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-7-1751289346-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458434%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20architects%20are%20also%20restoring%20the%20plinth%20around%20the%20building%20to%20keep%20water%20at%20bay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20it%20started%2C%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%20has%20braved%20bouts%20of%20unpredictable%20weather%2C%20but%20the%20usage%20of%20Adobe%20bricks%20(sun-dried%20bricks%20made%20from%20a%20mixture%20of%20earth%2C%20water%2C%20and%20a%20binding%20material%20like%20straw)%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20frequent%20water%20exposure%20is%20where%20the%20problem%20lies.%20Architect%20Sourabh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20over%20seven%20years%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20bricks%20have%20performed%20well%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20building%2C%20but%20in%20the%20toilet%20area%2C%20because%20of%20constant%20water%20exposure%2C%20their%20structural%20strength%20reduced%20and%20the%20wall%20collapsed.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20moisture%20intake%20is%20compounded%20by%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20black%20cotton%20soil%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20retain%20moisture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%20and%20his%20team%20are%20now%20attempting%20to%20restore%20the%20fallen%20structure%20using%20red%20brick%20and%20lime%20%E2%80%94%20still%20a%20sustainable%20option%20%E2%80%94%20but%20one%20more%20resistant%20to%20moisture.%20They%20are%20also%20restoring%20the%20plinth%20around%20the%20building%20to%20keep%20water%20at%20bay.%20Architecturally%2C%20this%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20the%20easiest%20process%2C%20architect%20Shaista%20Perveen%2C%20part%20of%20the%20restoration%20team%2C%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20work%20on%20traditional%20structures%2C%20we%20need%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20there%20is%20an%20integration%20between%20existing%20traditional%20material%20that%20has%20been%20used.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20architects%20have%20formulated%20a%20plan%20of%20action%20using%20the%20original%20architectural%20and%20structural%20drawings%20from%20the%20Kamath%20Design%20Studio%