0this%20was%20serious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20was%20just%20fifteen%20minutes%20away%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20lifetime.%20I%20drifted%20in%20and%20out%20of%20consciousness%2C%20the%20world%20around%20me%20fading%20in%20and%20out%20like%20a%20radio%20losing%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20it%20all%2C%20I%20kept%20repeating%20one%20thing%20to%20myself%3A%20%3Cem%3Ebreathe%E2%80%A6%20just%20keep%20breathing%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Each%20breath%20felt%20like%20a%20battle%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20could%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20could%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWheeled%20into%20the%20emergency%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20comprehend%20and%20answer%20most%20of%20the%20questions%20that%20the%20doctors%20were%20asking%20me.%20I%20even%20remember%20giving%20my%20phone%20passcode%20to%20a%20colleague%20so%20they%20could%20call%20and%20inform%20my%20wife%20about%20my%20condition.%20My%20ECG%20was%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20was%C2%A0checked%2C%C2%A0and%20that%20was%20when%20they%20found%20that%20I%20had%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20wheeled%20into%20the%20operating%20theatre%2C%20and%20an%20emergency%20surgery%20was%20done.%20The%20pain%20that%20had%20started%20from%20my%20left%20hand%20had%20now%20spread%20all%20over%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20been%20given%20an%20electric%20shock.%20The%20LAD%20artery%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20three%20most%20important%20coronary%20arteries%20in%20the%20body%2C%20was%20completely%20blocked%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20mentioned%20post-surgery%20that%20what%20I%20had%20experienced%20was%20a%20major%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImmense%20pain%20during%20the%20surgery%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20pain%20I%20experienced%20all%20through%20is%20not%20something%20that%20I%20can%20even%20put%20in%20words.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20about%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20post-surgery%20that%20I%20felt%20some%20kind%20of%20relief%20from%20the%20pain.%20There%20were%20two%20stents%20that%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20LAD%20artery%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20angiography%20was%20done%2C%20there%20were%20other%20blockages%20also%20that%20were%20found.%20I%20had%20almost%2095%20per%20cent%20blockages%20in%20other%20arteries%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20I%20was%20advised%20to%20go%20through%20yet%20another%20angioplasty%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20fix%20those%20blockages%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20surgeries%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20various%20medications%2C%20and%20I%20pop%20in%20at%20least%20ten%20pills%20a%20day%20now.%20From%20medicines%20for%20blood%20pressure%20to%20cholesterol%20and%20blood%20thinners%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prescribed%20so%20many.%20None%20of%20which%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20pre-surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EI%20was%20fairly%20fit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20overweight.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20lean%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20my%20BMI%20was%2025%20%E2%80%94%20well%20within%20what%E2%80%99s%20considered%20the%20normal%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20all%20outward%20appearances%2C%20I%20looked%20healthy.%20No%20one%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20I%20%E2%80%94%20would%E2%80%99ve%20guessed%20that%20I%20was%20at%20risk.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fit%20the%20image%20most%20people%20have%20of%20someone%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20attack.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20made%20it%20so%20easy%20to%20overlook%20the%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-