20my%20heart%20attack%2C%20doctors%20mentioned%20that%20I%20was%20perhaps%20confusing%20the%20angina%20pain%20to%20be%20acidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20entire%20experience%20was%20a%20harsh%20reminder%20of%20how%20easily%20we%20take%20our%20bodies%20for%20granted.%20We%20grow%20up%20believing%20that%20serious%20health%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20heart%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20are%20something%20that%20happen%20only%20after%2040%20or%2045.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20mindful%20about%20my%20fitness%2C%20careful%20about%20what%20I%20ate%2C%20and%20did%20everything%20I%20thought%20was%20%E2%80%9Cright.%E2%80%9D%20And%20yet%2C%20I%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20at%2033.%20It%20shattered%20the%20illusion%20that%20age%20or%20lifestyle%20alone%20can%20shield%20us%20from%20what%E2%80%99s%20brewing%20beneath%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Six%20months%20after%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20heart%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458077%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%2