ning.%20Loyal%20and%20constant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20what%20felt%20like%20forever%2C%20my%20thoughts%20weren%E2%80%99t%20in%20all-caps.%20There%20was%20no%20mental%20noise%2C%20no%20%E2%80%9Cding!%E2%80%9D%20to%20interrupt.%20My%20mind%2C%20for%20once%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20trying%20to%20swipe%20on%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20some%20dramatic%20epiphany%20about%20the%20universe%20or%20decide%20to%20become%20a%20forest%20monk.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20delete%20my%20accounts%20or%20vow%20to%20only%20communicate%20via%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328785%2Fimportant-letters-from-nehru-gandhi-sigmund-freud-that-shaped-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandwritten%20letters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20I%20did%20feel%20a%20quiet%20sort%20of%20okay-ness.%20Like%20maybe%20my%20brain%20had%20finally%20unclenched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bar%20was%20low%2C%20but%20that%20felt%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20morning%20after%20rebooting%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20woke%20up%20on%20a%20detox%20feeling%20like%20I%E2%80%99d%20been%20rebooted.%20Not%20transformed%20into%20a%20better%20person%20or%20anything%20extreme%20%E2%80%94%20just%E2%80%A6%20slightly%20more%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20reinstalled%20Instagram%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20bumping%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328356%2Fhyderabad-recykal-marketplace-sell-waste-online-empower-scrap-dealers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eold%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%E2%80%99ve%20outgrown%20a%20little.%20Familiar.%20A%20little%20annoying.%20Still%20kind%20of%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20checked%20my%20direct%20messages!.%20Responded%20to%20two%20reels.%20Sent%20a%20raccoon%20video%20to%20a%20friend.%20Th